<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
    <head>
        <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
        <title>配信設定 - 熱中症警戒アラート</title>
        <!-- Bootstrap -->
        <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-EVSTQN3/azprG1Anm3QDgpJLIm9Nao0Yz1ztcQTwFspd3yD65VohhpuuCOmLASjC" crossorigin="anonymous">
        <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-MrcW6ZMFYlzcLA8Nl+NtUVF0sA7MsXsP1UyJoMp4YLEuNSfAP+JcXn/tWtIaxVXM" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    </head>
    <body>
        <% if (process.env.NODE_ENV !== 'production') { %>
        <!-- VConsole -->
        <script src="https://unpkg.com/vconsole@latest/dist/vconsole.min.js"></script>
        <script>
            // VConsole will be exported to `window.VConsole` by default.
            var vConsole = new window.VConsole();
        </script>
        <% } %>

        <!-- WOFF SDK -->
        <script charset="utf-8" src="https://static.worksmobile.net/static/wm/woff/edge/3.6/sdk.js"></script>
        <!-- axios -->
        <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/axios/dist/axios.min.js"></script>

        <div class="container-fluid">

            <div id="groupWoffLoginButtons" class="row p-1" hidden>
                <div class="col">
                    <!-- LOGIN LOGOUT BUTTONS -->
                    <div class="buttonGroup">
                        <button id="woffLoginButton" class="btn btn-outline-primary">Log in</button>
                        <button id="woffLogoutButton" class="btn btn-outline-primary">Log out</button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="row p-1">
                <div class="col">
                    通知を受け取りたい都道府県等と暑さ指数を指定してください。<br>
                    ※ 設定した都道府県等のいずれかの観測地点で設定した暑さ指数を超える場合、通知します。
                </div>
            </div>

            <div id="loadingArea">
                読み込み中...
            </div>
            <div id="settingArea" hidden>
                <div class="row p-1">
                    <div class="col">
                        <!-- 都道府県 -->
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label class="fw-bold" for="selectPrefecture">都道府県等</label>
                            <select class="form-select" id="selectPrefecture">
                            </select>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="row p-1">
                    <div class="col">
                        <!-- 通知するレベル -->
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label class="fw-bold" for="selectAlertLevel">通知する暑さ指数</label>
                            <select class="form-select" id="selectAlertLevel">
                            </select>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="row p-1">
                    <div class="col">
                        <button class="btn btn-outline-dark" id="buttonSubmit">登録</button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </body>
</html>
